  "title": "Brand Communication Lead",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong>:</p><p><strong>Influencer & Creator Engagement</strong></p><ul><li>Lead influencer and creator programmes across Instagram, TikTok and Xiaohongshu (RedNote) to drive brand awareness and social advocacy.</li><li>Identify, recruit and manage relationships with influencers (macro & micro) and media partners, ensuring a healthy and scalable creator pipeline.</li><li>Develop clear creative briefs and oversee content delivery to ensure alignment with brand messaging, aesthetic standards, and campaign objectives.</li><li>Track and analyze collaboration outcomes using social performance indicators and ROI-related insights to optimise future influencer planning.</li></ul><p><strong>Brand Messaging & Copy Governance</strong></p><ul><li>Maintain and enforce brand messaging and tone of voice, keeping a centralised knowledge base and     messaging guidelines for the market.</li><li>Craft and localise high-quality copy for official social channels, website content and PR materials, ensuring a consistent brand voice across English and Mandarin platforms.</li><li>Empower frontline teams by developing customer-friendly scripts and FAQs for sales and operations,     ensuring a unified customer experience.</li></ul><p><strong>Public Relations & Reputation Management</strong></p><ul><li>Oversee digital reputation across global and regional platforms (e.g. Google, Dianping), with a focus on enhancing store ratings and consumer trust.</li><li>Coordinate PR communications and brand campaigns, including media relations and post-event amplification.</li><li>Monitor brand sentiment and community feedback, escalating risks and aligning response approaches when     required.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>3–6 years of experience in PR, Marketing Communications or Influencer Marketing within Retail sectors or a related field</li><li>Strong professional proficiency in English and Mandarin, with experience managing bilingual platforms. Mandarin proficiency is preferred to support platform moderation and communication where required for Xiaohongshu (RedNote).</li><li>Proven experience building and scaling influencer or creator programmes</li><li>Strong aesthetic sensitivity and attention to detail (copy and content quality)</li><li>Comfortable working cross-functionally in a fast-paced retail environment</li></ul>",
